OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly low cloud across
OL,6,FGloucestershire and Wiltshire soon
OL,7,Fclearing to leave hot sunshine. Higher
OL,8,Fcloud making sunshine hazy at times
OL,9,Felsewhere, with the chance of showers
OL,10,Fand isolated thunderstorms affecting
OL,11,Fsouthern Cornwall and Devon. Breezy
OL,12,Faround coasts.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FShowers in the far south
OL,15,Fmostly fading to leave a largely dry
OL,16,Fnight with clear spells and variable
OL,17,Fcloud. Winds steadily easing. A warm
OL,18,Fnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
