OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FFurther showers and the odd
OL,6,Fthunderstorm could fringe the far
OL,7,Fsouth. Many others remaining dry with
OL,8,Fbright or sunny spells and feeling hot
OL,9,Fwhere these are prolonged in the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FLargely
OL,12,Fdry and settled into the weekend.
OL,13,FFurther sunny spells, though cloud
OL,14,Famounts generally increasing.
OL,15,FTemperatures slowly dropping, but
OL,16,Fstill feeling warm in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
